{"id": "flp1665702599747", "title": "$keycheck", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "ProcScript Reference", "ProcScript: Functions", "$keycheck"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/flp1665702599747.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">$keycheck</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous:   $keyboard \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous:   $keyboard \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zbn1665702665252.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next:   $keyfields \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next:   $keyfields \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dmp1665702603557.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/flp1665702599747.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/flp1665702599747.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/flp1665702599747.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527569\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527569\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104flp1665702599747.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/flp1665702599747.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/flp1665702599747.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"flp1665702599747\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $keycheck\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"flp1665702599747___keycheck_271475\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Indicate whether a specified primary or candidate key should be validated.\n \n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"flp1665702599747__topic_d85178e1_d85179e1_d85180e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"flp1665702599747__p_d85181e1_d85182e1_d85183e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keycheck</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">KeyNumber</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"flp1665702599747__p_d85184e1_d85185e1_d85186e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keycheck</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">KeyNumber</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"flp1665702599747__p_d85187e1_d85188e1_d85189e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">set</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">reset</code>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keycheck</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">KeyNumber</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"flp1665702599747__section_w195ab1b7b5_w196ab1b7_w197ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"flp1665702599747__p_d85190e1_d85191e1_d85192e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">$keycheck(\"CUSTOMER\", 1)= 1</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"flp1665702599747__topic_d56537e1_d56538e1_d56539e1_d56540e1_d56541e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d640534e147\">\n                       Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"flp1665702599747__d6103e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"flp1665702599747__d6103e20__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"flp1665702599747__d6103e20__entry__2\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"flp1665702599747__d6103e20__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"flp1665702599747__d6103e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"flp1665702599747__d6103e20__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"flp1665702599747__d6103e20__entry__3\">Entity name.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"flp1665702599747__d6103e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">KeyNumber</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"flp1665702599747__d6103e20__entry__2\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"flp1665702599747__d6103e20__entry__3\"> Key identifier; the value will be\n\t\t\t\t truncated to form an integer. <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"flp1665702599747__d6103e80\">1, the primary key.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"flp1665702599747__d6103e83\">2, 3, 4, and so on, the number that\n\t\t\t\t\t\tidentifies a candidate key that has been defined for <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>. </li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"flp1665702599747__topic_d56542e1_d56543e1_d56544e1_d56545e1_d56546e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d640534e228\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8921e1_d8922e1_d8923e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keycheck</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8921e1_d8922e1_d8923e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8921e1_d8922e1_d8923e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8921e1_d8922e1_d8923e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8921e1_d8922e1_d8923e1__entry__2\">\n Key checking is not enabled.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8921e1_d8922e1_d8923e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8921e1_d8922e1_d8923e1__entry__2\">\n Key checking is currently enabled.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8924e1_d8925e1_d8926e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> when a value is assigned to\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keycheck</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8924e1_d8925e1_d8926e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8924e1_d8925e1_d8926e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8924e1_d8925e1_d8926e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"\"</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8924e1_d8925e1_d8926e1__entry__2\">\n Key checking could not be enabled because an error occurred. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains the exact error.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8924e1_d8925e1_d8926e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8924e1_d8925e1_d8926e1__entry__2\">\n key checking was successfully enabled.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"flp1665702599747__p_d85199e1_d85200e1_d85201e1\">If an error occurs, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8927e1_d8928e1_d8929e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 4. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following this\n            Function</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8927e1_d8928e1_d8929e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8927e1_d8928e1_d8929e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\"> Error constant </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8927e1_d8928e1_d8929e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> Meaning </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8927e1_d8928e1_d8929e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1102</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8927e1_d8928e1_d8929e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_ENTITY&gt; </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8927e1_d8928e1_d8929e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> The entity name provided is not a valid\n\t\t\t\t name or the entity is not present in the component structure. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8927e1_d8928e1_d8929e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1104</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8927e1_d8928e1_d8929e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_KEY&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8927e1_d8928e1_d8929e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> The specified key is not valid; for\n\t\t\t\t example, the key number was out of range. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8927e1_d8928e1_d8929e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1128</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8927e1_d8928e1_d8929e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_NOT_A_KEY&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"flp1665702599747__table_d8927e1_d8928e1_d8929e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> The specified key is an index.\n\t\t\t\t </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"flp1665702599747__topic_d56547e1_d56548e1_d56549e1_d56550e1_d56551e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d640534e477\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"flp1665702599747__d6417e20\">Allowed in all component types, except self-contained Reports.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"flp1665702599747__topic_d56552e1_d56553e1_d56554e1_d56555e1_d56556e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d640534e486\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"flp1665702599747__p_d85211e1_d85212e1_d85213e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keycheck</span> function returns a value that indicates whether the developer intends for validation to be carried out for the specified key the next time that it can occur. If <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keycheck</span> indicates that validation is demanded, the validation is performed regardless of whether validation is actually required. (Validation is required when both <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keymod</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keyvalidation</span> are 1, indicating that the key has been modified, but has not yet been validated.)</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"flp1665702599747__p_d85214e1_d85215e1_d85216e1\">Validation can occur when the user leaves all fields of the key (for example, with ^NEXT_FIELD, ^PREV_FIELD, or a mouse click); when an explicit validation statement is encountered (for example, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">validatekey</span>); or when a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">store</span> statement is encountered. It includes syntax checks on the fields comprising the key, activation of the validateKey trigger, and, in forms only, activation of the leaveModifiedKey trigger. After validation completes, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keycheck</span> is set to 0.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"flp1665702599747__p_d85217e1_d85218e1_d85219e1\">You can also use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keycheck</span> as the target in the left-hand side of an assignment. Set <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keycheck</span> to 1 to require checking for the specified key; set it to 0 to let Uniface take responsibility for validation. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$keycheck = !$keycheck\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"flp1665702599747__p_d85220e1_d85221e1_d85222e1\">Because <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keycheck</span> is essentially a Boolean function, when <var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var> evaluates to a non-zero value, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keycheck</span> becomes 1.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"flp1665702599747__section_jfr_fbb_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d640534e544\">Example: Checking for Keys</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example shows this function being used in the getFocus\n               trigger of an entity:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"flp1665702599747__pre_ubd_gbb_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger getFocus\n $keycheck(CUST_NUMBER.CUSTOMER, 1)= 1 ; check of primary key needed\n set $keycheck(CUST_NUMBER.CUSTOMER, 2) ; check of candidate key needed\nend; getFocus</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lrk1665702576500.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Validate</a><p>Determines whether the valerr data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are True or False (default).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jwi1665702576586.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validatefield</a><p>Validate a field of the current occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fdp1665702576817.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validatekey</a><p>Validate a key of the current occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bwv1665702576896.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validateocc</a><p>Validate an occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/swr1665702599962.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldcheck</a><p>Return or set the requirement for field validation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ogw1665702600188.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldendmod</a><p>Return the modification status of a field when the field is exited.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rjy1665702601052.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldmod</a><p>Return the modification status of a field.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qdc1665702602510.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldvalidation</a><p>Identify whether a field requires validation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hnz1719661363571.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$occcheck</a><p>Return or set the requirement for checking an occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eai1665702600334.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$occmod</a><p>Return the modification status of an occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fpz1719812992669.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$occvalidation</a><p>Check whether an occurrence requires validation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/emi1665702599671.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger leaveModifiedKey</a><p>Location for ProcScript that determines what happens after a key (especially a compound key) of an occurrence is modified. Applicable only in form components.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/frh1665703129863.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger validateKey</a><p>System trigger that defines the procedural checks to validate a modified primary or candidate key.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527569\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527569\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$keycheck Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $keycheck Indicate whether a specified primary or candidate key should be validated. $keycheck ( Entity , KeyNumber ) $keycheck ( Entity , KeyNumber ) = Expression set | reset $keycheck ( Entity , KeyNumber ) Example: $keycheck(\"CUSTOMER\", 1)= 1 Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Entity name. KeyNumber Numeric Key identifier; the value will be truncated to form an integer. 1, the primary key. 2, 3, 4, and so on, the number that identifies a candidate key that has been defined for Entity . Return Values Table 2. Values returned in $keycheck Value Meaning 0 Key checking is not enabled. 1 Key checking is currently enabled. Table 3. Values returned in $status when a value is assigned to $keycheck Value Meaning \"\" Key checking could not be enabled because an error occurred. $procerror contains the exact error. 1 key checking was successfully enabled. If an error occurs, $procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error. Table 4. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following this Function Value Error constant Meaning -1102 <UPROCERR_ENTITY> The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not present in the component structure. -1104 <UPROCERR_KEY> The specified key is not valid; for example, the key number was out of range. -1128 <UPROCERR_NOT_A_KEY> The specified key is an index. Use Allowed in all component types, except self-contained Reports. Description The $keycheck function returns a value that indicates whether the developer intends for validation to be carried out for the specified key the next time that it can occur. If $keycheck indicates that validation is demanded, the validation is performed regardless of whether validation is actually required. (Validation is required when both $keymod and $keyvalidation are 1, indicating that the key has been modified, but has not yet been validated.) Validation can occur when the user leaves all fields of the key (for example, with ^NEXT_FIELD, ^PREV_FIELD, or a mouse click); when an explicit validation statement is encountered (for example, validatekey ); or when a store statement is encountered. It includes syntax checks on the fields comprising the key, activation of the validateKey trigger, and, in forms only, activation of the leaveModifiedKey trigger. After validation completes, $keycheck is set to 0. You can also use $keycheck as the target in the left-hand side of an assignment. Set $keycheck to 1 to require checking for the specified key; set it to 0 to let Uniface take responsibility for validation. For example: $keycheck = !$keycheck Copy Because $keycheck is essentially a Boolean function, when Expression evaluates to a non-zero value, $keycheck becomes 1. Example: Checking for Keys The following example shows this function being used in the getFocus trigger of an entity: trigger getFocus $keycheck(CUST_NUMBER.CUSTOMER, 1)= 1 ; check of primary key needed set $keycheck(CUST_NUMBER.CUSTOMER, 2) ; check of candidate key needed end; getFocus Copy Related Links Validate Determines whether the valerr data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are True or False (default). validatefield Validate a field of the current occurrence. validatekey Validate a key of the current occurrence. validateocc Validate an occurrence. $fieldcheck Return or set the requirement for field validation. $fieldendmod Return the modification status of a field when the field is exited. $fieldmod Return the modification status of a field. $fieldvalidation Identify whether a field requires validation. $occcheck Return or set the requirement for checking an occurrence. $occmod Return the modification status of an occurrence. $occvalidation Check whether an occurrence requires validation. trigger leaveModifiedKey Location for ProcScript that determines what happens after a key (especially a compound key) of an occurrence is modified. Applicable only in form components. trigger validateKey System trigger that defines the procedural checks to validate a modified primary or candidate key. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}